| Route | Method | Role | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| [requirements/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/requirements/route.ts) | GET, POST | Admin/Teacher | List & create requirements |
| [requirements/[id]/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/requirements/%5Bid%5D/route.ts) | GET, PUT, DELETE | Admin/Teacher | Single requirement CRUD + stats |
| [submissions/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/route.ts) | GET | Admin/Teacher | Paginated submissions list |
| [submissions/[id]/review/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/%5Bid%5D/review/route.ts) | PUT | Admin/Teacher | Approve/reject with comment |
| [submissions/[id]/download/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/documents/submissions/%5Bid%5D/download/route.ts) | GET | Admin/Teacher | Secure file download |
| [student/documents/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/route.ts) | GET | Student | Scoped requirements + status |
| [student/documents/upload/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/documents/upload/route.ts) | POST | Student | Cloudinary upload + resubmit |

